metadata.name: START HERE, a sonic odyssey (a trailer)
metadata.description: Stimulated by the iconic renaissance of Downtown '81, "START HERE” is LATASHÁ's self-reflective audio-visual agglomeration through her evolving mythology, taking her listener and viewer through her existential breakthrough and dreamscapes meeting reality. With use of muse performance, electronica, hip hop, jazz, soul, poetry and world sound, Latashá brings us on a journey through her many-selves to find a oneness. A conversation in womanhood, Blackness, spirituality, creativity and evolution, "START HERE" is Latashá's starter map into self exploration, love and trust.
